  variations:
  - parent: {fileID: 11400000}
    sequence:
    - "Yeah\u2026 cool. Appreciate it. "
    - "Honestly, it\u2019s been one of those mornings, you know?"
    - " Lots of\u2026 paperwork. But hey, this helps. Definitely helps."
    categories: 0
  - parent: {fileID: 11400000}
    sequence:
    - 'Alright, sounds good. Thanks. '
    - "Uh\u2026 so, do you guys\u2026 ever get\u2026 like, a really busy shift? "
    - "I mean, it\u2019s fine, just curious."
    categories: 0
  - parent: {fileID: 11400000}
    sequence:
    - "Sweet. Thanks. Honestly, I don\u2019t usually\u2026 stop for lunch, but today\u2026 "
    - seemed like a good idea. Glad I did.
    categories: 0
  - parent: {fileID: 11400000}
    sequence:
    - 'Perfect. Appreciate it. '
    - "You know, I\u2019ve walked past this place a million times and\u2026 yeah,
      finally came in. "
    - So, here we are.
    categories: 0
  - parent: {fileID: 11400000}
    sequence:
    - 'Thanks a lot. '
    - "Uh\u2026 you\u2019re used to weird orders, right? "
    - "Because, yeah, this is probably\u2026 not standard."
